des:
Listen to daily fishing and spearfishing tips from experts around the world packed into short episodes. 

This podcast makes it easy for beginners to advanced fishermen and spearos to learn something new every day. A wise person once said, "go to bed smarter than when you woke up." With this daily short skill, we help you achieve it.

We cover surf fishing, spearfishing, inshore and offshore, fly fishing, bass fishign, and everything in between. We'll also bring on culinary experts to show you how to make the most of the fish you decide to keep.

For more detailed fishing guides, check out: https://castandspear.com/
